329
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,600
he stopped sending them?

330
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,330
Impossible.

331
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:20,240
Liu Rong and Yin Haohan seem to have a deep bond.

332
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,200
If she wanted to hide an affair,

333
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,080
she wouldn't have told us

334
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,480
about the flowers.

335
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,800
I think there are other possibilities.

336
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:27,660
Think about it.

337
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:28,520
Yin Haohan

338
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,720
secretly kept so many anonymous cards.

339
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:33,360
That shows he really minded this.

340
00:13:33,760 --> 00:13:35,960
Someone kept showing affection to Liu Rong.

341
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,720
Even on their wedding anniversary,

342
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,250
they chose to send flowers.

343
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,500
That's a bit provocative.

344
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:42,560
As a man,

345
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,520
wouldn't he be curious about who it was?

346
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:47,600
Even when he found out who it was,

347
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,440
he would choose to confront them.

348
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,520
So this person sending flowers

349
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,720
is currently the only one likely

350
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,650
to have a conflict with Yin Haohan.

351
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:56,170
Let's go inside and take a look.

352
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,840
I wrote this card by hand.

353
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,520
Because I wrote it so many times,

354
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,780
I remember it clearly.

355
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,280
But the exact time,

356
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,600
I can't remember clearly.

357
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,320
Before August 2016.

358
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,320
Identical cards,

359
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:09,800
you must have written them many times.

360
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:10,920
The flowers were the same, too.

361
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:11,580
Pink roses.

362
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:13,040
On July 6 of the same year,

363
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:14,560
you delivered flowers to Bailu Restaurant.

364
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:15,280
2016.

365
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,140
Bailu Restaurant.

366
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,440
I'll have to check the order records.

367
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,040
Not sure if I still have them.

368
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,120
Yin Haohan.

369
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,740
He bought flowers on July 7th.

370
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,040
This guy,

371
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:43,170
do you remember him?

372
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,240
Him?

373
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,600
He came here before to question me,

374
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:49,320
asking who ordered flowers for his wife.

375
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:51,440
He insisted on getting the sender's contact info.

376
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,040
He even topped up 5,000 yuan.

377
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:55,240
So I agreed to give him the sender's info.

378
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,700
Ever since he got the card,

379
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:57,920
