380
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,960
Do you still have that person's contact info?

381
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,820
It's long gone.

382
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,960
It was written in this notebook,

383
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,000
