392
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,060
It is on the way.

393
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,600
So, how is the investigation going?

394
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,530
We found out that

395
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:24,240
