396
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,800
On the day Yin Haohan disappeared,

397
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,560
he went to the flower shop,

398
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:27,760
got the contact info,

399
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:28,400
and immediately

400
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,600
went to find this man.

401
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,020
A love rival, then.

402
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,120
But

403
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,250
where did they meet?

404
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:34,720
We don't know that.

405
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,320
Anyway,

406
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,320
that day, Yin Haohan

407
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:37,560
got off work an hour early.

408
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:39,240
He said he was meeting a client,

409
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:41,040
