410
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:41,840
How do you know

411
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,760
that they definitely

412
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:43,320
met?

413
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:44,320
That man,

414
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,320
ever since Yin Haohan disappeared,

